The adjacent suburb of Cronulla offers several enclosed ocean pools, and many elegant restaurants and cafes. There is so much to enjoy in one of Sydney’s most upbeat and scenically beautiful southern suburbs.

The “Ocean Edition” at Shearwater Landing comprises a unique limited offering of large beachside lots, all with uninterrupted panoramic views over the Pacific Ocean, on the foreshore of Sydney’s newest coastal suburb, Greenhills Beach.
